---
title: Chermoula-Spiced Chicken & Garlic Yoghurt with Veggie Medley & Toasted Almonds
description: For tonight’s dinner, we’ve enlisted the help of our lively Middle Eastern-inspired chermoula spice blend: it coats
each bite of tender chicken breast in vibrant, earthy flavours and pairs perfectly with the robust roast roast veggie medly. Go for your life!

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
